Package: treeplyr
Type: Package
Title: An R Package for Using \code{dplyr} on Matched Tree and Data Objects
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-02-28
Author: Josef Uyeda
Maintainer: Josef Uyeda <josef.uyeda@gmail.com>
Description: This R package that matches phylogenetic trees and trait data, and
    allows dplyr-like manipulation of tree and data.
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3
Depends:
    ape (>= 3.0-6),
    dplyr,
    R (>= 2.15.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.10.3),
    lazyeval, 
    phytools,
    geiger
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
